name: Honey Stinger Almond Butter Dark Chocolate Organic Cracker
categories: Almond Butter Dark Chocolate Organic Cracker
description: Rich organic almond butter and honey sandwiched in hearty multigrain crackers and covered in a rich dark chocolate. As a bonus, the dark chocolate coating helps prevent cracker breakage and excessive crumbs, functional chocolate, what a concept!Ingredients: organic dark chocolate (organic cane sugar, organic chocolate liquor, organic cocoa butter, organic soy lecithin added as an emulsifier and organic vanilla), organic multi-grain cracker with sea salt (organic wheat flour, organic canola oil, organic cracked wheat, organic spelt, organic rye, organic barley, organic triticale, organic oats, organic flax, organic sesame seeds, organic sugar, sea salt and organic yeast), organic almond butter (organic almonds and organic palm oil), organic honey.Allergens – contains: soy, wheat and almonds.Made in a facility that processes: peanuts, egg, coconut, milk and other tree nuts.
